## Tech stack (PRD)

| Area | Technology | Role |
|------|------------|------|
| App shell | Expo (Dev Build) | Native modules, EAS builds |
| Navigation | React Navigation | Stack / tab / modal flows |
| UI state | Zustand | Fast, atomic selectors with `useShallow` |
| Persistent data | WatermelonDB | Offline-first entities (entries, goals, capsules, badges) |
| Fast cache | react-native-mmkv | Timers, streak display cache, session flags |
| Camera | react-native-vision-camera | Video/photo capture |
| Media processing | FFmpegKit (or maintained fork) | Trim, merge, assemble locally |
| Notifications | Notifee | Local + push channels, scheduling |
| AI | OpenAI API (Whisper / GPT) | Speech-to-text, emotion tagging, companion copy |
| Files | expo-file-system (or equivalent) | Document vs cache paths for media |

